1
00:00:05,560 --> 00:00:08,650
<font size="20"><b><font color="#333433">Sunday</font></b></font>

2
00:00:24,790 --> 00:00:26,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Your Majesty.</font>

3
00:00:26,940 --> 00:00:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, Kanadge.</font>

4
00:00:29,380 --> 00:00:33,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since we're working on a weekend, 
let's head straight to the venue.</font>

5
00:00:33,930 --> 00:00:35,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

6
00:00:38,260 --> 00:00:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He made sure to recline the seat.</i></font>

7
00:00:43,100 --> 00:00:45,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How considerate of you, Kanadge.</font>

8
00:00:45,400 --> 00:00:46,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you!</font>

9
00:00:49,710 --> 00:00:56,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When traveling by car, the Hell-Lord 
must always sit in a fully-reclined seat.</i></font>

10
00:00:56,110 --> 00:00:57,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As for the reason why...</i></font>

11
00:00:58,860 --> 00:01:01,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>To avoid this!</i></font>

12
00:01:01,070 --> 00:01:05,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>By the way, this is 
a Hellhorde company car.</i></font>

13
00:02:36,170 --> 00:02:38,010
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="32">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

14
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:40,260
<font size="20">{\an7}<font color="#9d9ea2">m 0 0 l 230 0 230 80 0 80</font></font>

15
00:02:38,010 --> 00:02:40,260
<font size="20"><font size="11"><font color="#3f4346"><font face="Times New Roman">{\an8}Hellhorde Performance Award Speech
 Don't forget to smile!
 Thank you all for gathering here today 
for the Hellhorde Performance Award Ceremony.
 (Make sure to pause!)
 To foster further growth and
peace in the Demon World, 
the members of the Hellhorde spare
 no effort working diligently daily, 
in the area best suited to their talents.
 <font color="#4d1c2a">* Take a breath. Calm yourself!
 <font color="#3f4346">Among them, the people we recognize 
today have made significant 
contributions to the Hellhorde this quarter.</font></font></font></font></font></font>

16
00:02:40,790 --> 00:02:45,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have you memorized your speech for 
the Hellhorde Performance Award Ceremony?</font>

17
00:02:45,320 --> 00:02:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, barely.</font>

18
00:02:48,260 --> 00:02:51,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But I'm getting nervous.</font>

19
00:02:52,160 --> 00:02:53,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know you'll do great.</font>

20
00:02:55,490 --> 00:02:56,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh.</font>

21
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:59,440
<font size="20"><b><font size="6"><font color="#575a45">Drive-Thru</font></font></b></font>

22
00:02:56,650 --> 00:02:58,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There's a Mark D's. 
Should we stop to eat here?</font>

23
00:02:59,440 --> 00:03:02,280
<font size="20"><b><font color="#474c4d">Drive-Thru</font></b></font>

24
00:02:59,720 --> 00:03:04,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I remember Your Majesty saying you 
wanted to try their limited-time burger.</font>

25
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's fine, but thank you.</font>

26
00:03:07,910 --> 00:03:10,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got no appetite right now 
with these nerves.</font>

27
00:03:11,330 --> 00:03:14,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to mention the item 
I was interested in...</font>

28
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:17,750
<font size="20"><font color="#7f220e"><b>Grand Croquette Burger</b></font></font>

29
00:03:14,000 --> 00:03:17,750
<font size="20"><font color="#7f220e"><b>Grand Croquette Burger</b></font></font>

30
00:03:14,010 --> 00:03:17,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">is only sold on their lunch menu.</font>

31
00:03:17,760 --> 00:03:21,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right, they're still on 
their breakfast menu right now.</font>

32
00:03:22,050 --> 00:03:26,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although the breakfast menu 
is great in its own right.</font>

33
00:03:26,030 --> 00:03:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's true.</font>

34
00:03:29,420 --> 00:03:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know the one they have 
with a meat patty between two pancakes?</font>

35
00:03:32,850 --> 00:03:35,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. I love it.</font>

36
00:03:36,080 --> 00:03:41,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love putting the hash brown you get 
with the meal <i>inside</i> the sandwich.</font>

37
00:03:42,620 --> 00:03:48,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sweet and salty goodness, 
plus the hash brown's crispy texture...</font>

38
00:03:48,060 --> 00:03:49,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the best.</font>

39
00:04:01,290 --> 00:04:02,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey...</font>

40
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would you say 
that after we've passed it?</font>

41
00:04:07,450 --> 00:04:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry.</font>

42
00:04:11,710 --> 00:04:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to eat it really badly now.</font>

43
00:04:16,180 --> 00:04:17,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I turn back?</font>

44
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, we've almost made it to the venue.</font>

45
00:04:20,460 --> 00:04:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's keep going.</font>

46
00:04:22,720 --> 00:04:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry.</font>

47
00:04:28,200 --> 00:04:31,290
<font size="20"><font color="#2a3738"><b>{\an9}Demon World Cultural Center</b></font></font>

48
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:31,290
<font size="20"><font color="#fafafc"><b>{\an9}West Parking Lot</b></font></font>

49
00:04:32,770 --> 00:04:35,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It looks like there's 
a corner store nearby.</font>

50
00:04:35,430 --> 00:04:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you need me to get you anything?</font>

51
00:04:38,160 --> 00:04:39,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Majesty?</font>

52
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:43,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That Mark Dragon is around 
a kilometer away.</font>

53
00:04:43,420 --> 00:04:45,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Two kilometers for a round trip.</font>

54
00:04:45,510 --> 00:04:49,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My body should be able to 
withstand that distance.</font>

55
00:04:49,610 --> 00:04:50,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

56
00:04:58,620 --> 00:05:02,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hell-Lord Speed Form!</font>

57
00:04:59,150 --> 00:05:02,440
<font size="20"><b><font color="#314a1e"><font size="35"><font face="Georgia">Hell-Lord Speed Form</font></font></font></b></font>

58
00:05:04,670 --> 00:05:06,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna go stop by the Mark Dragon.</font>

59
00:05:12,700 --> 00:05:15,460
<font size="20"><b><font size="15"><font color="#42463a">Drive-Thru</font></font></b></font>

60
00:05:15,450 --> 00:05:18,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will this be for take-out or dine-in?</font>

61
00:05:18,180 --> 00:05:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So that'll be one cheeseburger?</font>

62
00:05:20,550 --> 00:05:22,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like fries with that?</font>

63
00:05:28,380 --> 00:05:33,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put the hash brown between 
the patty and the egg...</font>

64
00:05:34,300 --> 00:05:35,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I go.</font>

65
00:05:42,500 --> 00:05:44,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Delicious!</font>

66
00:05:44,710 --> 00:05:50,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Immediately after biting into 
the fluffy pancake and juicy patty,</i></font>

67
00:05:50,390 --> 00:05:53,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I get the crunch from the hash brown...</i></font>

68
00:05:54,150 --> 00:05:56,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What an exciting surprise.</i></font>

69
00:05:56,580 --> 00:05:59,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My fangs are crying in joy!</i></font>

70
00:06:00,270 --> 00:06:03,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The rich, slightly melted cheese...</i></font>

71
00:06:03,240 --> 00:06:06,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that firm egg is great, too.</i></font>

72
00:06:06,190 --> 00:06:09,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Which will you get, 
the whites or the yolk?</i></font>

73
00:06:09,970 --> 00:06:14,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's a matter of taste, but I get
a little happy when it's the yolk.</i></font>

74
00:06:15,020 --> 00:06:16,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You could say that...</i></font>

75
00:06:16,790 --> 00:06:19,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>All of the ingredients 
are in perfect unity.</i></font>

76
00:06:19,810 --> 00:06:22,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A quintuple combo of delicious.</i></font>

77
00:06:23,590 --> 00:06:25,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not a single weak spot.</i></font>

78
00:06:26,460 --> 00:06:29,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Truly splendid!</i></font>

79
00:06:29,310 --> 00:06:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm glad you like it.</font>

80
00:06:32,710 --> 00:06:35,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really does taste 
good eating it like this.</font>

81
00:06:37,760 --> 00:06:41,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was so nervous 
that I couldn't eat breakfast,</font>

82
00:06:41,180 --> 00:06:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but thanks to you, I regained my appetite 
and shook off my nerves.</font>

83
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:48,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Kanadge.</font>

84
00:06:48,470 --> 00:06:52,220
<font size="20">{\an7}<font color="#e8e8e8">m 0 0 l 230 0 230 80 0 80</font></font>

85
00:06:48,470 --> 00:06:52,220
<font size="20"><font size="11"><font color="#202020"><font face="Times New Roman">{\an8}Hellhorde Performance Award Speech
 Don't forget to smile!
 Thank you all for gathering here today 
for the Hellhorde Performance Award Ceremony.
 (Make sure to pause!)
 To foster further growth and
peace in the Demon World, 
the members of the Hellhorde spare
 no effort working diligently daily, 
in the area best suited to their talents.
 <font color="#a03d52">* Take a breath. Calm yourself!
 <font color="#202020">Among them, the people we recognize 
today have made significant 
contributions to the Hellhorde this quarter.</font></font></font></font></font></font>

86
00:06:48,940 --> 00:06:51,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll knock 'em dead.</font>

87
00:06:52,220 --> 00:06:56,220
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="20">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

88
00:06:52,220 --> 00:06:56,220
<font size="20"><b><font face="Verdana"><font size="15">{\an7}<font color="#f2bc69">Aside from Speed Form, the Hell-Lord 
has multiple forms, such as Attack Form
 and Defense Form</font></font></font></b></font>

89
00:06:56,310 --> 00:06:58,680
<font size="20"><b><font color="#333231"><font size="15">Meanwhile</font></font></b></font>

90
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:03,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Today is Sunday. 
Since there's no torture today...</i></font>

91
00:07:08,280 --> 00:07:11,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The gang is here for some bowling.</i></font>

92
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

93
00:07:20,420 --> 00:07:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good luck, Princess-chan.</font>

94
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just relax.</font>

95
00:07:24,930 --> 00:07:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bowling? I know the rules, at least.</font>

96
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:32,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You throw the ball down there 
and try to get the highest score, right?</font>

97
00:07:32,520 --> 00:07:33,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's right.</font>

98
00:07:36,380 --> 00:07:37,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness?!</font>

99
00:07:37,310 --> 00:07:39,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go!</font>

100
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,810
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="25"><font color="#2b3335">Prin-Prin








Vanillucky</font></font></b></font>

101
00:07:43,820 --> 00:07:45,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! I got a goal!</font>

102
00:07:45,630 --> 00:07:47,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The G stands for "gutter ball."</font>

103
00:07:47,300 --> 00:07:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never seen a gutter ball like that.</font>

104
00:07:49,320 --> 00:07:52,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't know the rules at all, huh?</font>

105
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it, Princess.</font>

106
00:07:54,420 --> 00:07:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't launch the 
ball through the air.</font>

107
00:07:56,300 --> 00:07:59,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The objective is to roll the ball 
to knock down the pins that are lined up.</font>

108
00:07:59,910 --> 00:08:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, really?</font>

109
00:08:03,240 --> 00:08:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me show you how it's done.</font>

110
00:08:05,580 --> 00:08:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be taking over 
for your second roll, Princess.</font>

111
00:08:08,550 --> 00:08:09,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Second roll?</font>

112
00:08:09,760 --> 00:08:14,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, place your fingers inside the 
ball's three holes and take position.</font>

113
00:08:14,290 --> 00:08:17,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's dead serious, 
even when it's just a game.</i></font>

114
00:08:15,370 --> 00:08:17,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The standard is a four-step approach.</font>

115
00:08:17,130 --> 00:08:20,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's the Senpai I know! 
I'm learning so much!</i></font>

116
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:23,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Begin your swing on the second step.</font>

117
00:08:23,600 --> 00:08:25,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't exert too much energy here.</font>

118
00:08:25,800 --> 00:08:30,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let the ball's weight do the work, 
with your shoulder acting as a pivot.</font>

119
00:08:31,100 --> 00:08:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the third step, your arm 
should reach its highest point.</font>

120
00:08:34,810 --> 00:08:38,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On the fourth step, bend your left 
knee as you firmly plant your foot.</font>

121
00:08:38,410 --> 00:08:42,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Think of it as shifting your weight 
from the right leg to the left one.</font>

122
00:08:42,240 --> 00:08:44,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Follow through and release the ball.</font>

123
00:08:51,720 --> 00:08:54,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is it okay that you 
didn't knock down any pins?</font>

124
00:08:54,020 --> 00:08:56,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't the point to knock them down?</font>

125
00:08:56,100 --> 00:08:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Well? Well?</font>

126
00:08:58,050 --> 00:08:58,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well?</font>

127
00:08:58,810 --> 00:09:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Shut your mouth!</font>

128
00:09:00,050 --> 00:09:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Why are you mad at me?</font>

129
00:09:03,790 --> 00:09:06,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That one's on you, Princess-chan.</font>

130
00:09:06,350 --> 00:09:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I agree.</font>

131
00:09:07,860 --> 00:09:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness is at fault.</font>

132
00:09:09,560 --> 00:09:11,730
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="25"><font color="#2b3335">Prin-Prin









Vanillucky</font></font></b></font>

133
00:09:12,050 --> 00:09:13,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So be it.</font>

134
00:09:14,440 --> 00:09:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let me, of the noble House of Peschutz, 
teach you how it's played!</font>

135
00:09:19,440 --> 00:09:21,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You brought your own ball and glove...</font>

136
00:09:21,620 --> 00:09:24,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you a pretty experienced bowler?!</font>

137
00:09:24,120 --> 00:09:26,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope! I just bought these!</font>

138
00:09:26,580 --> 00:09:28,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you just like to look the part!</font>

139
00:09:32,750 --> 00:09:34,710
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font size="25"><font color="#2b3335">Prin-Prin










Vanillucky</font></font></b></font>

140
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:38,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to look cool 
in front of the princess...</font>

141
00:09:38,770 --> 00:09:40,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay strong, Vanilla-senpai!</font>

142
00:09:42,520 --> 00:09:44,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

143
00:09:44,290 --> 00:09:50,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, let a former school basketball 
player show you how it's really done.</font>

144
00:09:50,250 --> 00:09:51,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not playing basketball.</font>

145
00:09:51,560 --> 00:09:55,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, but my bowling skills come 
from being on the basketball team!</font>

146
00:09:55,280 --> 00:09:58,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Family restaurants! Karaoke! Bowling!</font>

147
00:09:58,470 --> 00:10:01,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The three main places you can find every 
basketball player in the world!</font>

148
00:10:01,330 --> 00:10:03,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're insulting all 
the basketball players!</font>

149
00:10:03,390 --> 00:10:06,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here I go! The true power of someone 
who was on the basketball team!</font>

150
00:10:13,590 --> 00:10:14,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking good.</font>

151
00:10:14,890 --> 00:10:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Next I'll aim for the right, 
with a little bit of spin...</font>

152
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:21,260
<font size="20"><b><font size="20"><font color="#2f393a">{\an8}Vanillucky













youk












<font size="15">
<font size="20">In-In</font></font></font></font></b></font>

153
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:23,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! How do you like <i>that</i>?!</font>

154
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:27,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No real opinions 
to offer one way or another.</font>

155
00:10:30,530 --> 00:10:33,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looks like I'm up next.</font>

156
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There!</font>

157
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:39,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In-chan threw it with both hands.</font>

158
00:10:39,920 --> 00:10:41,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that allowed?</font>

159
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:44,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're mostly free to throw 
the ball however you like.</font>

160
00:10:44,150 --> 00:10:49,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, you'll find it's not so easy to 
knock down the pins without proper form.</font>

161
00:10:49,910 --> 00:10:51,670
<font size="20"><b><font size="16"><font color="#333333">The only thing she has is proper form</font></font></b></font>

162
00:10:53,120 --> 00:10:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Got a strike!</font>

163
00:10:58,880 --> 00:11:01,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-The game's only just begun!</font>

164
00:11:01,710 --> 00:11:03,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

165
00:11:13,010 --> 00:11:14,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi-yah!</font>

166
00:11:29,580 --> 00:11:32,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They all had fun.</i></font>

167
00:11:33,020 --> 00:11:34,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why?</font>

168
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,460
<font size="20"><font size="7"><font color="#46ded6"><b>Demon World Ristorante e Caffè</b></font></font></font>

169
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,460
<font size="20"><font size="15"><font color="#c27974"><b>Sayizatso</b></font></font></font>

170
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,460
<font size="20"><font size="9"><font color="#51535c"><font face="Georgia"><b>Hell-Lord Pharmacy</b></font></font></font></font>

171
00:11:34,960 --> 00:11:37,460
<font size="20"><font size="9"><font color="#f9f8f6">Prescriptions Filled Here</font></font></font>

172
00:11:41,430 --> 00:11:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Did you find them?</font>

173
00:11:44,230 --> 00:11:47,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found the spot here with the eyeball...</font>

174
00:11:49,790 --> 00:11:52,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's where things start getting hard.</font>

175
00:11:52,070 --> 00:11:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, found it! Here!</font>

176
00:11:53,710 --> 00:11:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

177
00:11:53,890 --> 00:11:56,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're right! The clouds are different!</font>

178
00:11:56,520 --> 00:12:00,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They also enjoyed 
the spot-the-difference puzzle.</i></font>

179
00:12:02,710 --> 00:12:05,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, why?</font>

180
00:12:08,950 --> 00:12:11,000
<font size="20"><b><font color="#d01c76">{\an8}<font size="22">'Tis Time for <font color="#020000">"Torture,"
<font color="#cf1374">Princess</font></font></font></font></b></font>

181
00:12:20,720 --> 00:12:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is really amazing.</font>

182
00:12:22,910 --> 00:12:25,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nah, it's not a big deal...</font>

183
00:12:27,520 --> 00:12:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yoo-hoo. What are you up to?</font>

184
00:12:30,660 --> 00:12:31,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Mama.</font>

185
00:12:32,620 --> 00:12:35,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Vanilla, can I show this to Master Mama?</font>

186
00:12:35,910 --> 00:12:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure...</font>

187
00:12:37,230 --> 00:12:41,320
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="30"><font color="#4e94e6">The <font color="#30cb36">Eli<font color="#e00a2b">te <font color="#4e94e6">Li'l <font color="#30cb36">Kitt<font color="#e00a2b">y</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

188
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look, Vanilla made this picture book!</font>

189
00:12:40,040 --> 00:12:41,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? That's amazing!</font>

190
00:12:41,310 --> 00:12:43,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You published a picture book?</font>

191
00:12:43,060 --> 00:12:47,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I found a printing service that
lets you print books in small batches,</font>

192
00:12:47,680 --> 00:12:49,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I used it to make this.</font>

193
00:12:49,180 --> 00:12:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, that's incredible.</font>

194
00:12:51,100 --> 00:12:54,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The drawings are so cute. 
I could swear it was professional.</font>

195
00:12:55,790 --> 00:12:59,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my dream to put out 
a real picture book someday.</font>

196
00:12:59,290 --> 00:13:00,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's great.</font>

197
00:13:00,760 --> 00:13:03,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It just so happens that picture books 
are why I'm here today.</font>

198
00:13:03,700 --> 00:13:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

199
00:13:04,550 --> 00:13:10,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A Hellhorde employee in my year later 
quit to become a picture book author.</font>

200
00:13:10,890 --> 00:13:16,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He won a newcomer award some time ago, 
so we're celebrating with drinks.</font>

201
00:13:16,640 --> 00:13:18,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gekkou...</font>

202
00:13:18,220 --> 00:13:19,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know him?</font>

203
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yeah...</font>

204
00:13:21,660 --> 00:13:26,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They released his book that won 
the award, so I read it, too.</font>

205
00:13:26,040 --> 00:13:27,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really liked it.</font>

206
00:13:27,610 --> 00:13:29,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You follow his work!</font>

207
00:13:30,020 --> 00:13:31,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I read about him in an interview.</i></font>

208
00:13:31,970 --> 00:13:35,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He said that he wrote tons 
of picture books while working.</i></font>

209
00:13:35,190 --> 00:13:36,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want to ask him about that...</i></font>

210
00:13:36,900 --> 00:13:41,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If possible, I want him to read my book 
and give me his thoughts.</i></font>

211
00:13:41,800 --> 00:13:46,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But I'm sure I'd just be bothering him...</i></font>

212
00:13:46,060 --> 00:13:48,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Would you like to meet Gekkou, then?</font>

213
00:13:48,590 --> 00:13:49,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

214
00:13:49,550 --> 00:13:52,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know he'd love to hear 
how you felt about his book.</font>

215
00:13:52,420 --> 00:13:54,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You could show him your 
picture book as well.</font>

216
00:13:59,560 --> 00:14:02,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. It's fine.</font>

217
00:14:02,380 --> 00:14:03,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure?</font>

218
00:14:03,940 --> 00:14:06,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd be too embarrassed 
to have him read it.</font>

219
00:14:08,100 --> 00:14:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh...</font>

220
00:14:10,010 --> 00:14:11,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll see you around.</font>

221
00:14:11,530 --> 00:14:12,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah!</font>

222
00:14:20,260 --> 00:14:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you sure about this, Vanilla-chan?</font>

223
00:14:23,180 --> 00:14:26,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd feel bad intruding 
on their celebration.</font>

224
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:32,430
<font size="20">{\an5}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="30"><font color="#4e94e6">The <font color="#30cb36">Eli<font color="#e00a2b">te <font color="#4e94e6">Li'l <font color="#30cb36">Kitt<font color="#e00a2b">y</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

225
00:14:26,760 --> 00:14:29,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the idea of showing it 
to a pro author...</font>

226
00:14:29,810 --> 00:14:31,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just made this as a hobby...</font>

227
00:14:32,420 --> 00:14:36,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, it's just a hobby, 
not to mention it sucks.</font>

228
00:14:37,230 --> 00:14:39,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I don't have the talent...</font>

229
00:14:39,910 --> 00:14:45,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it takes courage, not talent, 
to make your dreams come true.</font>

230
00:14:52,640 --> 00:14:53,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Giant!</font>

231
00:14:55,060 --> 00:14:57,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rats! She's gone!</font>

232
00:14:57,110 --> 00:15:01,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Her long stride means she walks fast 
when she's by herself!</font>

233
00:14:58,290 --> 00:14:58,870
<font size="20"><b><font color="#374a8a">Stomp</font></b></font>

234
00:14:58,790 --> 00:14:59,370
<font size="20"><b><font color="#374a8a">Stomp</font></b></font>

235
00:14:59,290 --> 00:14:59,870
<font size="20"><b><font color="#374a8a">Stomp</font></b></font>

236
00:14:59,790 --> 00:15:00,370
<font size="20"><b><font color="#374a8a">Stomp</font></b></font>

237
00:15:00,290 --> 00:15:00,870
<font size="20"><b><font color="#374a8a">Stomp</font></b></font>

238
00:15:00,790 --> 00:15:01,040
<font size="20"><b><font color="#374a8a">Stomp</font></b></font>

239
00:15:02,370 --> 00:15:03,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've got this!</font>

240
00:15:03,970 --> 00:15:06,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Mama!</font>

241
00:15:10,580 --> 00:15:12,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">G-Gekkou.</font>

242
00:15:12,800 --> 00:15:18,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I liked your newcomer award-winning
 book, <i>What's a Ninja?</i> a lot.</font>

243
00:15:18,110 --> 00:15:19,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really look up to you!</font>

244
00:15:19,540 --> 00:15:22,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Look up to me? I'm not sure how to react.</font>

245
00:15:22,230 --> 00:15:24,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, thank you. 
I'm really glad to hear that.</font>

246
00:15:24,970 --> 00:15:28,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A-And, well...</font>

247
00:15:29,560 --> 00:15:33,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I wrote this picture book.</font>

248
00:15:33,180 --> 00:15:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You wrote this?</font>

249
00:15:34,510 --> 00:15:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

250
00:15:35,950 --> 00:15:39,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my dream to become 
a picture book author like you.</font>

251
00:15:39,330 --> 00:15:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Could you take a look at it?</font>

252
00:15:41,990 --> 00:15:44,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course. It'd be an honor.</font>

253
00:15:53,490 --> 00:15:55,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a wonderful thing to have a dream.</font>

254
00:15:55,670 --> 00:15:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

255
00:15:57,550 --> 00:15:59,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your dream, Master Mama?</font>

256
00:16:00,140 --> 00:16:01,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My dream?</font>

257
00:16:03,510 --> 00:16:05,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't have one!</font>

258
00:16:04,770 --> 00:16:06,520
<font size="20">{\an9}<b><font color="#e91b77">Bam</font></b></font>

259
00:16:05,100 --> 00:16:06,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't?</font>

260
00:16:06,520 --> 00:16:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm happy just enjoying 
every day to its fullest.</font>

261
00:16:10,930 --> 00:16:14,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's lovely having a dream, 
but you can have fun without one.</font>

262
00:16:15,850 --> 00:16:17,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess you're right.</font>

263
00:16:17,210 --> 00:16:18,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Princess!</font>

264
00:16:21,080 --> 00:16:22,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How'd it go?</font>

265
00:16:22,890 --> 00:16:25,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want to write more now!</font>

266
00:16:26,250 --> 00:16:28,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'd love to read more from you!</font>

267
00:16:30,000 --> 00:16:35,380
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="30"><font color="#4e94e6">The <font color="#30cb36">Eli<font color="#e00a2b">te <font color="#4e94e6">Li'l <font color="#30cb36">Kitt<font color="#e00a2b">y</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

268
00:16:35,380 --> 00:16:38,430
<font size="20">{\an8}<b><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font size="30"><font color="#4e94e6">The <font color="#30cb36">Eli<font color="#e00a2b">te <font color="#4e94e6">Li'l <font color="#30cb36">Kitt<font color="#e00a2b">y</font></font></font></font></font></font></font></font></b></font>

269
00:16:35,970 --> 00:16:37,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Elite Li'l Kitty.</i></font>

270
00:16:39,780 --> 00:16:44,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The elite li'l kitty was better 
at everything than all the others.</i></font>

271
00:16:45,530 --> 00:16:47,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She was always first by a mile!</i></font>

272
00:16:46,730 --> 00:16:53,360
<font size="20"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#282828"><b>Award</b></font></font></font>

273
00:16:48,930 --> 00:16:51,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No one else could even hope 
to compete with her.</i></font>

274
00:16:53,490 --> 00:16:59,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But no matter how many times she 
came in first or got compliments,</i></font>

275
00:16:59,310 --> 00:17:01,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she still felt weird and wiggly inside.</i></font>

276
00:17:02,540 --> 00:17:04,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Until one day...</i></font>

277
00:17:06,470 --> 00:17:09,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The li'l kitty made a friend!</i></font>

278
00:17:10,590 --> 00:17:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The li'l kitty had fun doing all 
sorts of things with her friend.</i></font>

279
00:17:16,800 --> 00:17:22,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The li'l kitty found out how happy 
it made her being with someone else.</i></font>

280
00:17:23,020 --> 00:17:26,980
<font size="20"><b><font size="35"><font face="Comic Sans MS"><font color="#2a2a2a">The End</font></font></font></b></font>

281
00:17:24,080 --> 00:17:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The end.</i></font>

282
00:17:35,900 --> 00:17:39,030
