Sho Stifler</font></font></font></font>

284
00:18:57,030 --> 00:18:59,530
<font size="20"><b><font color="#8dc456">Chuo Hellway</font></b></font>

285
00:18:57,030 --> 00:18:59,530
<font size="20"><b><font color="#f7fbed">Hellholm</font></b></font>

286
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:05,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The National Inquisitors Conference 
ran longer than scheduled,</i></font>

287
00:19:05,930 --> 00:19:07,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and now it's gotten late.</i></font>

288
00:19:08,330 --> 00:19:12,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Perhaps I should have booked a hotel, 
like His Majesty suggested.</i></font>

289
00:19:12,960 --> 00:19:16,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, I was planning to go see 
Mille-chan's baby tomorrow!</font>

290
00:19:16,830 --> 00:19:18,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I must return home tonight!</font>

291
00:19:20,400 --> 00:19:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A rest stop?</font>

292
00:19:22,700 --> 00:19:26,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should take a short break 
and grab some coffee.</font>

293
00:19:30,880 --> 00:19:35,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Rest stops these days are
getting more and more luxurious.</i></font>

294
00:19:35,160 --> 00:19:39,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I haven't been to one with just bathrooms 
and vending machines in ages.</i></font>

295
00:19:40,240 --> 00:19:42,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Time for some coffee...</i></font>

296
00:19:42,350 --> 00:19:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I don't believe it!</font>

297
00:19:44,910 --> 00:19:46,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hot snacks!</font>

298
00:19:46,600 --> 00:19:47,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And this here is...</font>

299
00:19:48,230 --> 00:19:50,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An instant noodle vending 
machine you don't see anymore!</font>

300
00:19:50,480 --> 00:19:52,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And one for soba and udon!</font>

301
00:19:52,330 --> 00:19:56,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is the last place one would expect 
to find all this treasure!</font>

302
00:19:56,120 --> 00:19:59,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything this world has to 
offer is right here!</font>

303
00:19:59,340 --> 00:20:04,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So this is where the One Piece was, 
the greatest single treasure of them all!</font>

304
00:20:05,090 --> 00:20:08,010
<font size="20"><font size="8"><b><font color="#473d33">{\an8}Tasty potatoes deep-fried in oil.</font></b></font></font>

305
00:20:05,900 --> 00:20:08,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Let's start with some french fries.</i></font>

306
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Open the lid, being careful 
not to burn yourself...</i></font>

307
00:20:15,800 --> 00:20:19,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sprinkle the included salt 
packet unevenly on purpose,</i></font>

308
00:20:19,360 --> 00:20:21,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>creating pockets of salty 
and not-salty regions.</i></font>

309
00:20:26,360 --> 00:20:27,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They're great.</i></font>

310
00:20:28,230 --> 00:20:30,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You can really taste the potatoes.</i></font>

311
00:20:32,310 --> 00:20:35,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So salty! Jackpot.</i></font>

312
00:20:36,780 --> 00:20:41,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A way to enjoy fries that differs from 
the calculated taste at a restaurant.</i></font>

313
00:20:43,420 --> 00:20:45,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Next up is...</i></font>

314
00:20:45,800 --> 00:20:48,760
<font size="20"><b><font face="Georgia"><font size="17"><font color="#5c5c5d">Soba & Udon</font></font></font></b></font>

315
00:20:47,220 --> 00:20:48,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Some soba.</i></font>

316
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:52,060
<font size="20"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="14"><font color="#5a2f21">Tempura Udon</font></font></b></font></font>

317
00:20:48,760 --> 00:20:52,060
<font size="20"><font face="Georgia"><b><font size="14"><font color="#5a2f21">Tempura Soba</font></font></b></font></font>

318
00:20:58,510 --> 00:21:00,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's filled to the brim with broth.</font>

319
00:21:01,320 --> 00:21:04,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">These machines are old. 
It adds to the charm.</font>

320
00:21:24,240 --> 00:21:25,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's delicious.</font>

321
00:21:27,450 --> 00:21:29,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This soft and spongy mixed tempura...</i></font>

322
00:21:29,830 --> 00:21:32,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I enjoy a good, crispy 
tempura added at the end,</i></font>

323
00:21:32,270 --> 00:21:35,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but when it gets soft 
and soggy like this...</i></font>

324
00:21:35,960 --> 00:21:37,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I love that, too!</i></font>

325
00:21:39,400 --> 00:21:42,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can feel the flavor filling my mouth!</i></font>

326
00:21:43,500 --> 00:21:45,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This slightly cheap fish cake...</i></font>

327
00:21:46,310 --> 00:21:48,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But for this soba...</i></font>

328
00:21:50,580 --> 00:21:54,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yep, this is fine. The best, even!</i></font>

329
00:22:03,780 --> 00:22:05,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was great.</font>

330
00:22:08,540 --> 00:22:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's nothing but trees around us, 
so it's pitch-black outside.</i></font>

331
00:22:14,310 --> 00:22:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A world of total natural darkness, 
separated by bright artificial lights.</i></font>

332
00:22:20,070 --> 00:22:22,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It feels like I'm on a spaceship.</i></font>

333
00:22:39,120 --> 00:22:42,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wanted to try some 
instant noodles as well,</font>

334
00:22:42,080 --> 00:22:44,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I really have no room for them.</font>

335
00:22:44,760 --> 00:22:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even though instant noodles eaten outside 
are thirty percent tastier.</font>

336
00:22:50,510 --> 00:22:52,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Preferably with a fork 
against convention.</font>

337
00:22:53,960 --> 00:22:56,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I suppose I should get going.</font>

338
00:23:00,310 --> 00:23:02,810
<font size="20"><font color="#745c1a"><font size="10"><b>Hot and ready in sixty seconds.</b></font></font></font>

339
00:23:16,890 --> 00:23:18,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a souvenir.</i></font>

340
00:23:18,860 --> 00:23:20,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A late-night snack.</i></font>

341
00:23:20,510 --> 00:23:24,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You don't come across 
a piece of treasure like this very often.</i></font>

342
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:29,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Just a little more driving, 
and I'll be at Bonepile Junction.</i></font>

343
00:23:30,700 --> 00:23:32,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Off we go!</i></font>

